channel.title: Can someone help me identify this webcam?
channel.description:
I formatted my computer, and now I don't have the drivers for my webcam. Or the box or anything.
The webcam has no logo's and no writing on it. I don't have a clue what it is. I need to know the brand and the model so that I can download the drivers.
[img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/9615/webcamx.jpg[/img]
I wasn't sure if this should go into hardware or not.
